== UniversalLanguageSelector 2017.04 ==
Released at 2017-04-28.

=== Noteworthy changes ===
* Bartosz Dziewoński fixed language change tooltip position. (T161203)
* Niklas Laxström added link to Compact Language Links info page in the beta
feature description.
* Niklas Laxström fixed broken site picks feature for Compact Language Links.
(T157344)

=== Fonts ===
* Kartik Mistry added Sundanese (su) font. (T162221)

=== Input methods ===
* Amir Aharoni fixed name of Arabic keyboard.
* Amir Aharoni and Felix Nartey added keyboard for Ga language.
* Amir Aharoni added Akan keyboard also for Twi language.
* fgaim added new IMEs for Eritrean languages: Tigrinya (ti), Tigre (tig),
Blin (byn).
* WikiDiscoverer fixed autonym for Gõychi Konknni (gom) language.
